name: SNK Officially Authorized The King of Fighters NFT

metadata.name: SNK Officially Authorized The King of Fighters NFT
metadata.description:
"The King of Fighters" - NFT, is a collection of 6500 items promoted by Trade3.0.

Trade3.0 is the first NFT Launchpad, focused on issuance, trading, and utility. Our team also develops a legal currency transaction module, allowing everyone to participate in "trading" and enjoy "Web3". Our business scope includes authorized IP, incubation projects, legal currency support, etc. 

"The King of Fighters" - NFT, the series characters are authorized by SNK.
